| `resolve_model()` with tier downgrade walk | `backend/src/relay/config.rs:548-586` |
| `generate_default_agents_with_source()` | `backend/src/relay/config.rs:449-490` |
| `load_or_generate_agent_configs()` | `backend/src/relay/config.rs:498-527` |
| `AgentConfigDto` with `model_tier` | `frontend/src/composables/useAgentConfigs.ts:8-21` |
| `ModelDefinition` interface | `frontend/src/composables/useApiSources.ts:6-10` |
